      "text": "builder.goals from \u0027probes/hint/\u0027, write to %goals%",
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "indent": 0,
      "comment": "Even though file.read.Build() infers \u0022csv\u0022 from the literal \u0027.csv\u0027\nextension, the user (type) hint \u0022json\u0022 on the variable.set wins.\nDownstream snapshot reads %x%(json) \u2014 Build() never stamps when an\nexplicit Type slot already exists (StampOnTerminalVariableSet:577).",
